{"type":"answer","id":9085,"parentType":"question","parentId":2066,"uid":1441,"contents":"梁家河阅览室的主要藏书区域在二楼，因此进门就是一间通往二楼的宏伟的楼梯厅。楼梯厅雕梁画栋，以多种珍贵大理石装饰，两侧布满精美的雕塑。尤其引人注目的是天花板正中描绘史诗英雄萨格尔王加冕的巨幅天顶画。<br>\n<br>\n来到二楼，经过一间奢华的绿色前厅，即到达了梁家河阅览室的核心——三间藏书房，整整200斤书都保存于此。<br>\n<br>\n在藏书房后面，还有两间读书沙龙、一间休息室，均装潢精致优美。<br>\n<br>\n而令人奇怪的是，在梁家河阅览室的一个不起眼角落有扇门，门后还有一间十分隐蔽但极为精美的卧室。梁家河阅览室管理人员介绍，当初刁大犬总书记还在村里当支部书记时，白天扛麦子，晚上就来阅览室彻夜读书。许多村民被其刻苦所打动，悄悄集资为他在阅览室里修了一间卧室。从此以后，小卧室里时常传来大犬刻苦读书悬梁刺股的呻吟。<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/79c1bc5545e5f6a7d5b901e4cdc0cf44.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/79c1bc5545e5f6a7d5b901e4cdc0cf44.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/79c1bc5545e5f6a7d5b901e4cdc0cf44.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/1b6f9746706840151a363344531aa195.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/1b6f9746706840151a363344531aa195.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/1b6f9746706840151a363344531aa195.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/d93779813477a72028ffc11628b8878c.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/d93779813477a72028ffc11628b8878c.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/d93779813477a72028ffc11628b8878c.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/e2d2fe4cb1178875b482cf56e295ab93.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/e2d2fe4cb1178875b482cf56e295ab93.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/e2d2fe4cb1178875b482cf56e295ab93.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/c37d5b22d60ed643fd438b3da3c1ed8c.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/c37d5b22d60ed643fd438b3da3c1ed8c.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/c37d5b22d60ed643fd438b3da3c1ed8c.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/bf2e553db9c530d4af7a92ebaa077992.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/bf2e553db9c530d4af7a92ebaa077992.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/bf2e553db9c530d4af7a92ebaa077992.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/85595d12828309d764848b23060e30fa.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/85595d12828309d764848b23060e30fa.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/85595d12828309d764848b23060e30fa.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/6b91f8ea3ea4e2bf9d712ea3c678c002.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/6b91f8ea3ea4e2bf9d712ea3c678c002.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180724/6b91f8ea3ea4e2bf9d712ea3c678c002.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-07-25","agreeCount":6,"discussionCount":0}